eadlineLovebirds\" />\n*''[[Time to Hunt (film)|Time to Hunt]]'' \u2013 Theatrical release cancelled and to be released on Netflix on April 10, 2020.<ref>{{cite web|first=Yeon-soo|last=Kwak|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2020/03/689_286633.html|title='Time to Hunt' skips theaters and goes straight to Netflix|date=March 23, 2020|website=[[The Korea Times]]|accessdate=March 24, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324084152/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2020/03/689_286633.html|archive-date=March 24, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Trolls World Tour]]'' \u2013 Theatrical release cancelled and home on demand to be released on April 6, 2020 in Europe and April 10, 2020 in the United States.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Fuster |first1=Jeremy |title=Universal to Release 'Trolls World Tour' for Digital Rental on Same Day as Theatrical Release |url=https://www.thewrap.com/universal-to-release-trolls-world-tour-for-digital-rental-on-same-day-as-theatrical-release/ |accessdate=March 16, 2020 |work=[[TheWrap]] |date=March 16, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317184238/https://www.thewrap.com/universal-to-release-trolls-world-tour-for-digital-rental-on-same-day-as-theatrical-release/ |archive-date=March 17, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Ravindran |first1=Manori |title=Rakuten TV to Stream 'Trolls World Tour' in Europe Ahead of U.S. |url=https://variety.com/2020/biz/box-office/rakuten-tv-to-stream-trolls-world-tour-in-europe-ahead-of-u-s-1234570121/ |accessdate=April 4, 2020 |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=April 3, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403134807/https://variety.com/2020/biz/box-office/rakuten-tv-to-stream-trolls-world-tour-in-europe-ahead-of-u-s-1234570121/ |archive-date=April 3, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n=== Delayed ===\n<!-- Please insert in alphabetical order! Thanks! -->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#ffdead;\"\n! Film \n! Original re